'''Gaulians''' were the native inhabitants of [[Gaulus/Legends|Gaulus]]. During the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] maintained a [[Alliance Base 16|base]] on their planet, and negotiated with the Gaulians through a [[3PO-series protocol droid/Legends|3PO-series protocol droid]], which was eventually discovered to be an [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] [[espionage droid]].<ref name="Rebel">[[The Rebel Alliance Sourcebook (Second Edition)|''The Rebel Alliance Sourcebook'', Second Edition]]</ref>

